    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into quarters, then separate the wedges so you end up with a pile of onion petals</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/baked-greek-cheese-and-harissa-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into chunks</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>onion petals</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped pepper</strong> and <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> dried thyme </strong>with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/baked-greek-cheese-and-harissa-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Give everything a good mix up, then nestle your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> in the centre of the vegetables</p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook for 18-20 min or until the veg are tender and roasted</p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/baked-greek-cheese-and-harissa-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> in a large bowl and a small pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>- this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> and<strong> salad</strong> to the bowl with the dressing and toss \u2013 this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/baked-greek-cheese-and-harissa-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pasta </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> pasta </strong>for 7-9 min (10-12 min for wholewheat) or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>pasta </strong>, reserving 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/baked-greek-cheese-and-harissa-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> with the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>harissa stock</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/baked-greek-cheese-and-harissa-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables are roasted, add the <strong>harissa stock</strong> and give everything a good mix up until well combined</p><p>Top with the <strong>cooked pasta </strong>and<strong> spinach </strong>and return the dish to the oven for 3-5 min or until the spinach has wilted</p><p>Once the spinach has wilted, remove the dish from the oven, season with a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mix until fully combined \u2013 this is your <strong>baked Greek cheese & harissa pasta</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/baked-greek-cheese-and-harissa-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baked Greek cheese & harissa pasta </strong>with the<strong> dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
